'''飓风凯尔'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Kyle}}）是有纪录以来持续时间第五长的[[大西洋|大西洋]][[热带气旋|热带]]或[[副熱帶氣旋|亚热带气旋]]，也是[[2002年大西洋飓风季|2002年大西洋飓风季]]第11个获得命名的风暴和第3场飓风，于9月20日由[[百慕大|百慕大]][[罗盘方位|东南偏东]]方向的一股亚热带气旋发展而成。系统蜿蜒向西行进，先是转变成热带气旋，后又在9月25日增强为飓风。之后的两个星期时间里，凯尔总体向西移动，其强度因外界环境的变化出现了多次波动。10月11日，风暴转向东北并以热带风暴强度在[[南卡罗莱纳州|南卡罗莱纳州]]的[[查尔斯顿_(南卡罗来纳州)|查尔斯顿]]和[[北卡罗莱纳州|北卡罗莱纳州]]的[[長灘_(北卡羅萊納州)|长滩]]附近[[登陸_(氣象學)|登陆]]。10月12日，凯尔被一股逐渐逼近的[[冷锋|冷锋]]吸收而消散，这时其作为热带天气系统已经存在了22天。

这场飓风给百慕大带去了小幅降水，当地没有出现严重破坏。风暴两次登陆[[美国|美国]]，带去的中等程度降雨引起局部山洪爆发，还有多条道路封闭。南卡罗莱纳州有一家养老院和多套移动房屋中的居民因洪水而被迫撤离。凯尔还催生了至少4场[[龙卷风|龙卷风]]，其中一场袭击了南卡罗莱纳州的[[乔治敦_(南卡罗来纳州)|乔治敦]]，导致8人受伤，7幢建筑物被毁，还有106套受损。这场气旋一共造成了约500万[[美元|美元]]（2002年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|5000000|2002}}}}美元）的破坏，但没有直接引起人员丧生。不过，风暴的温带残留之后导致[[不列颠群岛|不列颠群岛]]近海间接有一人遇难。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Kyle 2002 track.png}}
9月15日，一股冷锋在[[百慕大|百慕大]]东南方向停止前进并开始减弱，于9月18日退化成[[低气压|低气压]]。9月18日，系统在西面一片[[低压槽|低压槽]]的辅助下发展出固有环流。[[对流|对流]]发展成远离中心的狭长[[雨带|带状特征]]，风暴的总体层次结构逐步改善。气象部门估计系统于9月20日晚在百慕大东南方向约789公里外海域发展成了第十二号亚热带低气压，将其分类为亚热带气旋主要是考虑到对流距离中心的距离。气旋南面存在上层低气压，北面也有一个低压槽，由此产生的弱转向气流令其转而北上。接下来低气压逐渐增强，于9月21日清晨成为亚热带风暴，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]因此将其命名给“凯尔”（{{lang|en|Kyle}}）。<ref name="tcr">{{cite web | author = Stacy R. Stewart | year = 2002 | title = Hurricane Kyle Tropical Cyclone Report | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-05-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140330144310/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/2002kyle.shtml | archivedate = 2014-03-30 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/2002kyle.shtml }}</ref>

亚热带风暴凯尔在获得命名后朝东北偏北方向前进，逐渐走出一个顺时针方向的环形路径<ref name="tcr" />。起初，环流中心部分从深层对流的南侧和西翼暴露在外<ref name="disc6">{{cite web | author = Jarvinen | year = 2002 | title = Subtropical Storm Kyle Discussion Six | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-05-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131112204630/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.006.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2013-11-12 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.006.html }}</ref>。9月22日，中心周围的对流有所增加，系统发展出暖心并因此获重新归类为热带气旋<ref name="tcr" />。由于北面有一个[[反气旋|反气旋]]逐渐形成，凯尔因此转向西南。经过短暂的减弱过程后<ref>{{cite web | author = Jarvinen | year = 2002 | title = Tropical Storm Kyle Discussion Ten | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-05-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131112204311/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.010.html | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.010.html | archivedate = 2013-11-12 }}</ref>，之前属中等强度的[[风切变|风切变]]开始减少，风暴对流因此得以深化，[[外流_(气象学)|外流]]也得到进一步发展<ref>{{cite web | author = Jarvinen | year = 2002 | title = Tropical Storm Kyle Discussion Fifteen | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-05-02 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.015.html | archivedate = 2013-11-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131112204340/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.015.html | deadurl = no }}</ref>。接下来凯尔因进入的海域[[海面温度|温度]]逐渐升高而增强，于9月24日晚开始发展出[[风眼|带状眼形特征]]<ref>{{cite web | author = Stewart | year = 2002 | title = Tropical Storm Kyle Discussion Seventeen | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-05-02 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.017.html | archivedate = 2013-11-12 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131112204507/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.017.html }}</ref>。之后风暴继续缓慢增强，于[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]9月25日正午12点达到飓风强度。次日，凯尔在百慕大东南偏东方向约789公里处达到风速每小时130公里的最高强度<ref name="tcr" />。
[[Image:TRMM_Kyle_2002.jpg|thumb]]}}[[卫星图像|卫星图像]]]]

飓风凯尔的最高强度保持了约24小时<ref name="tcr" />，然后在9月27日开始由于上层风切变增多导致外流受限，对流带出现扭曲而开始减弱<ref>{{cite web | author = Avila & Cobb | year = 2002 | title = Hurricane Kyle Discussion Twenty-Seven | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-05-02 | archivedate = 2012-10-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025085313/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.027.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.027.html }}</ref>，较为干燥的空气也对减弱过程起到了推动作用<ref>{{cite web | author = Franklin | year = 2002 | title = Hurricane Kyle Discussion Twenty-Nine | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-05-02 | archivedate = 2012-10-25 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025085320/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.029.html | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.029.html }}</ref>。9月28日，飓风在转向西北偏西后减弱到热带风暴强度<ref name="tcr" />，其中心到次日时已经从深层对流中暴露出来<ref>{{cite web | author = Molleda & Lawrence | year = 2002 | title = Tropical Storm Kyle Discussion Thirty-Four | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-05-02 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.034.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025094053/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.034.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-10-25 }}</ref>。接下来的几天时间里，风暴因北面有低压槽经过，并且西翼还有[[高压脊|高压脊]]逐渐发展出来而基本停止移动<ref>{{cite web | author = Franklin | year = 2002 | title = Tropical Storm Kyle Discussion Thirty-Five | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-05-02 | archivedate = 2012-10-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025094103/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.035.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.035.html }}</ref>。9月29日，系统中再次发展出[[雷暴|雷暴]]并由此暂时停止减弱<ref>{{cite web | author = Avila | year = 2002 | title = Tropical Storm Kyle Discussion Thirty-Six | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-05-02 | archivedate = 2012-10-25 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025094109/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.036.html | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.036.html }}</ref>，但到了次日清晨又开始减弱<ref>{{cite web | author = Beven | year = 2002 | title = Tropical Storm Kyle Discussion Thirty-Nine | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-05-02 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.039.html | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025094117/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.039.html | archivedate = 2012-10-25 }}</ref>，于9月30日晚降级成热带低气压<ref name="tcr" />。环流从东北向西南方向拉长，风暴的东北部分与逐渐逼近的锋带关联起来<ref name="disc41" />，气象部门曾通过监测短暂认为这一部分存在发展迹象<ref>{{cite report | author = Stewart | date = 2002-09-30 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>。但实际上却是风暴的西南区域重新发展出对流，并开始成为占主导地位的环流<ref name="disc41">{{cite web | author = Avila | year = 2002 | title = Tropical Depression Kyle Discussion Forty-One | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-05-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025094122/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.041.html | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.041.html | archivedate = 2012-10-25 }}</ref>。

在热带低气压强度下保持了约18小时后，系统中心东南部再度发展出一些雷暴<ref>{{cite web | author = Avila | year = 2002 | title = Tropical Storm Kyle Discussion Forty-Four | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-05-02 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.044.html | archivedate = 2012-10-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025094127/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.044.html | deadurl = no }}</ref>，然后于10月1日再度增强为热带风暴<ref name="tcr" />。虽然外界存在不利于其发展的风切变，但对流的层次仍逐渐获得改善，发展成[[雨带|雨带]]并将风暴的中层环流包裹起来<ref>{{cite web | author = Franklin | year = 2002 | title = Tropical Storm Kyle Discussion Forty-Eight | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-05-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025094132/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.048.html | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.048.html | archivedate = 2012-10-25 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。10月2日晚，凯尔的中心发展出一片眼状特征<ref name="disc49">{{cite web | author = Franklin | year = 2002 | title = Tropical Storm Kyle Discussion Forty-Nine | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-05-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025094140/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.049.html | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.049.html | archivedate = 2012-10-25 }}</ref>，风速也提高到约每小时105公里<ref name="tcr" />，气象部门在实际操作中预测，风暴将再次达到飓风强度<ref name="disc49" />。但实际上凯尔却于10月4日因遭遇更多的风切变导致中心从对流中暴露出来<ref>{{cite web | author = Stewart | year = 2002 | title = Tropical Storm Kyle Discussion Fifty-Four | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-05-02 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.054.html | archivedate = 2012-10-25 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025094145/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.054.html }}</ref>。对流开始变得时断时续，并从环流中分离出来<ref>{{cite web | author = Avila | year = 2002 | title = Tropical Storm Kyle Discussion Fifty-Six | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-05-02 | archivedate = 2012-10-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025094151/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.056.html | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.056.html | deadurl = no }}</ref>，风暴于10月5日再次降级成热带低气压，并在这一期间开始稳步向西北偏西方向移动，然后又缓慢朝东北偏北转向<ref name="tcr" />。10月6日，由于风切变有所减少，气旋得以在百慕大西北偏西方向475公里外洋面再度达到热带风暴强度。这一期间系统座落在一片存在弱转向气流的区域中，东北和西北方向存在高压脊，东南偏东方向有一股上层低气压，西北方向则存在一片广阔的低压槽<ref>{{cite web | author = Pasch & Mainelli | year = 2002 | title = Tropical Storm Kyle Discussion Sixty-Four | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-05-02 | archivedate = 2012-10-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025094157/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.064.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.064.html }}</ref>。到10月7日时，风暴已开始围绕西侧的高压脊缓慢向西南方向行进。由于干燥的空气限制了对流发展，环流逐渐变得拉长<ref>{{cite web | author = Pasch & Mainelli | year = 2002 | title = Tropical Storm Kyle Discussion Sixty-Eight | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-05-02 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.068.html | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025094205/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.068.html | archivedate = 2012-10-25 }}</ref>，再加上10月8日风切变再度增多的不利影响<ref>{{cite web | author = Pasch | year = 2002 | title = Tropical Storm Kyle Discussion Seventy-Two | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-05-02 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.072.html | archivedate = 2012-10-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025094244/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.072.html | deadurl = no }}</ref>，凯尔又一次减弱成热带低气压<ref name="tcr" />。

10月9日清晨，低气压中包含的环流中心已经不存在任何关联的深层对流，而深层对流正是风暴归类为热带天气系统的先决条件之一。多个[[热带气旋预报模型|飓风预报模型]]都认为，凯尔会逐渐减弱直至[[耗散|耗散]]<ref>{{cite web | author = Franklin | year = 2002 | title = Tropical Depression Kyle Discussion Seventy-Four | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-05-02 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.074.html | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025094318/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.074.html | archivedate = 2012-10-25 }}</ref>。在持续了24小时没有明显对流的状态后，低气压进入一片水温较高的海域，其中心东南部于10月10日再度有雷暴形成<ref>{{cite web | author = Franklin | year = 2002 | title = Tropical Depression Kyle Discussion Seventy-Eight | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-05-03 | archivedate = 2012-10-13 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121013001537/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.078.html | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.078.html }}</ref>。外界环境变得更有利于气旋发展，风切变和干燥空气均有所减少<ref>{{cite web | author = Beven | year = 2002 | title = Tropical Depression Kyle Discussion Seventy-Nine | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-05-03 | archivedate = 2012-10-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025094324/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.079.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.079.html }}</ref>。低气压继续围绕高压脊移动，先转向西进，再转朝西北偏西方向的[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]海岸逼近<ref>{{cite web | author = Pasch | year = 2002 | title = Tropical Depression Kyle Discussion Eighty-One | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-05-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025094329/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.081.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-10-25 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.081.html }}</ref>。10月11日，系统转向北上朝一片逼近的冷锋进发，对流也出现显著增长<ref>{{cite web | author = Franklin | year = 2002 | title = Tropical Depression Kyle Discussion Eighty-Two | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-05-03 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.082.html | archivedate = 2012-10-25 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025094333/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.082.html }}</ref>，风暴在佛罗里达州和[[乔治亚州|乔治亚州]]边境以东约60公里洋面又一次达到热带风暴强度<ref name="tcr" />。

[[Image:TS_Kyle_02_landfall.jpg|right]]
重新成为热带风暴后，凯尔略朝东北转向，与海岸线平行移动，在南卡罗莱纳州的[[麦克勒安威尔_(南卡罗莱纳州)|麦克勒安威尔]]附近以热带风暴的最低标准强度登陆。风暴一度短暂进入开放海域，但很快又于10月11日晚在北卡罗莱纳州长滩附近实现第二次登陆。10月12日清晨，风暴已减弱成热带低气压<ref name="tcr" />。在陆地上行进期间，低气压东北部存在一股与其分离的非热带低气压<ref>{{cite web | author = Franklin | year = 2002 | title = Tropical Depression Kyle Special Discussion Eighty-Six | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-05-03 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.086.html | archivedate = 2012-10-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025094338/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.086.html | deadurl = no }}</ref>，并且风切变也大幅增多，因此气象部门认为系统不大可能还能再度强化<ref>{{cite web | author = Franklin | year = 2002 | title = Tropical Depression Kyle Discussion Eighty-Seven | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-05-03 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.087.html | archivedate = 2012-10-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025094347/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.087.html | deadurl = no }}</ref>。但实际上对流却在逐渐逼近冷锋的影响下再度发展出[[斜压|斜压]]，凯尔也在北卡罗莱纳州的帕姆利科湾（{{lang|en|Pamlico Sound}}）东部上空第五次达到热带风暴强度<ref>{{cite web | author = Stewart | year = 2002 | title = Tropical Storm Kyle Discussion Eighty-Eight | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-05-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025094357/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.088.html | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.088.html | archivedate = 2012-10-25 }}</ref>。由于风场扩大，对流转变带锋带，这次增强只持续了很短的时间<ref>{{cite web | author = Avila | year = 2002 | title = Tropical Storm Kyle Discussion Eighty-Nine | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-05-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121001032123/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.089.html | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.089.html | archivedate = 2012-10-01 }}</ref>。进入[[大西洋|大西洋]]西部后，热带风暴凯尔于10月12日晚与一片冷锋融合<ref name="tcr" />，其残留继续向东行进，于10月14日走出一道环状路径后转向东北，之后在10月17日吹袭[[亚速尔群岛|亚速尔群岛]]。次日，这片残留由西北方向的一场[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]吸收，然后继续向东北移动，在10月23日到达[[不列颠群岛|不列颠群岛]]附近海域<ref name="gp">{{cite web | author = Kevin Boyle | year = 2002 | title = October 2002 Worldwide Tropical Summary | accessdate = 2014-05-03 | archivedate = 2011-06-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110605235509/http://australiasevereweather.com/cyclones/2003/summ0209.htm | url = http://www.australiasevereweather.com/cyclones/2003/summ0209.htm | publisher = Australian Severe Weather | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

== 防灾措施 ==
由于无法确认风暴动向，百慕大政府于9月30日向岛上发布了[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴观察预警]]，不过次日就予以中止<ref name="tcr" />。

随着凯尔逼近佛罗里达州海岸，美国国家飓风中心向[[可可比奇|可可比奇]]到乔治亚州[[布朗斯维克_(乔治亚州)|布朗斯维克]]（{{lang|en|Brunswick}}）之间地区发布了热带风暴观察预警，并在之后将预警范围向北延伸至南卡罗莱纳州的恐怖角（{{lang|en|Cape Fear}}），然后又经进一步调整，在警报范围中包括帕姆利科湾到北卡罗莱纳州[[瑟夫城|瑟夫城]]（{{lang|en|Surf City}}）之间沿海地区<ref name="tcr" />。风暴登陆前，[[美国国家气象局|美国国家气象局]]驻北卡罗莱纳州[[威尔明顿_(北卡罗莱纳州)|威尔明顿]]办事处向大部分沿海地区发布了洪水预警，这些区域之后也确实受到了影响。南卡罗莱纳州[[弗洛伦斯县_(南卡罗莱纳州)|弗洛伦斯县]]、[[威廉斯堡县_(南卡罗莱纳州)|威廉斯堡县]]和[[乔治敦县_(南卡罗莱纳州)|乔治敦县]]收到了防洪警报<ref name="nws1">{{cite web | author = Wilmington, North Carolina National Weather Service | year = 2002 | title = Statistics for Tropical Storm Kyle | accessdate = 2014-05-03 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | url = http://www.erh.noaa.gov/ilm/archive/10-11-02/kylestats.html | archivedate = 2012-08-05 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120805190607/http://www.erh.noaa.gov/ilm/archive/10-11-02/kylestats.html }}</ref>。该州的十个县宣布进入[[紧急状态|紧急状态]]<ref>{{cite press release|author=South Carolina State Register |year=2002 |title=Executive Orders from the Governor's Office |accessdate=2008-05-19 |format=DOC |url=http://167.7.215.69/register/index2002.doc }}{{dead link|date=六月 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot }}</ref>。

== 影响 ==
[[Image:Kyle_2002_rainfall.gif|thumb]]带去的降雨量统计数据。]]
百慕大在10月1至2日因风暴及其北面冷锋的共同影响而出现55.6毫米降水，相当于当地半个月的降雨量总和<ref>{{cite web | author = Bermuda Weather Service | date = 2002-11-04 | title = Weather Summary for October 2002 | accessdate = 2012-03-10 | url = http://www.weather.bm/data/2002-10.html | archivedate = 2012-03-10 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120310050136/http://www.weather.bm/data/2002-10.html }}</ref>。

凯尔在佛罗里达州东北近海经过期间给[[费南迪纳比奇_(佛罗里达州)|费南迪纳比奇]]带去了0.4米高的[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]。风力相对较小，[[圣奥古斯丁_(佛罗里达州)|圣奥古斯丁]]出现的最高阵风时速为52公里，费南迪纳比奇的降雨量达到52毫米<ref name="tcr" />。乔治亚州沿海地区出现中等程度降雨，[[亨特陆军机场|亨特陆军机场]]达到最高的136毫米<ref name="tcr" />。大部分降水都是在12小时内积累下来的，多条道路和一些低洼地区因此被淹，造成多个路段封闭，许多车辆被困<ref>{{cite report | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2002 | title = Event Report for Georgia}}</ref>。南卡罗莱纳州出现中等程度降水，降雨量最高的[[艾迪斯托海滩_(南卡罗莱纳州)|艾迪斯托海滩]]达到161毫米，在城区引起轻度洪灾<ref name="tcr" />。[[圣士提反_(南卡罗来纳州)|圣士提反]]及其周边道路和建筑物的洪水达到数英尺高，一家养老院为此被迫疏散<ref>{{cite report | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2002 | title = Event Report for South Carolina}}</ref>。[[曼宁_(南卡罗莱纳州)|曼宁]]有17套移动房屋受到洪水的严重破坏，迫使约50人转移到避难所<ref name="sc1">{{cite report | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2002 | title = Event Report for South Carolina (2)}}</ref>。[[佛罗伦萨_(南卡罗来纳州)|佛罗伦萨]]出现了十起[[交通事故|交通事故]]<ref>{{cite report | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2002 | title = Event Report for South Carolina (3)}}</ref>。这场热带风暴在乔治敦催生的一场{{lang|en|[[藤田级数|F2]]}}级龙卷风在陆地上行进了约2公里，龙卷风在最高强度时掀翻了五所移动房屋和一辆汽车<ref name="tor">{{cite web | author = Wilmington, North Carolina National Weather Service | year = 2002 | title = Preliminary Local Storm Report for Tornado Spawned by Tropical Storm Kyle | accessdate = 2014-05-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120805190612/http://www.erh.noaa.gov/ilm/archive/10-11-02/torstats.html | archivedate = 2012-08-05 | url = http://www.erh.noaa.gov/ilm/archive/10-11-02/torstats.html }}</ref>。龙卷风还摧毁了7套民房，令106套建筑物受到破坏，其中28个受损严重，还有8人受伤<ref>{{cite web | author = South Carolina State Climatology Office | year = 2002 | title = Tropical Storm Kyle in South Carolina | accessdate = 2014-05-03 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130210083742/http://www.dnr.sc.gov/climate/sco/Tropics/HurricaneReports/2002/hurricane_Kyle.php | url = http://www.dnr.sc.gov/climate/sco/Tropics/HurricaneReports/2002/hurricane_Kyle.php | archivedate = 2013-02-10 }}</ref>。
[[Image:Kyle_2002_SC_tornado_damage.jpg|right]]造成的破坏]]

北卡罗莱纳州因高于正常水平的潮汐导致了轻微的海滩侵蚀。[[格林维尔_(北卡罗莱纳州)|格林维尔]]沿海区域的降雨量达到142毫米<ref name="tcr" />。风暴带来的湿气令内陆降水增多，其中最高的[[巴特纳_(北卡罗莱纳州)|巴特纳]]（{{lang|en|Butner}}）达到221毫米<ref name="rain">{{cite web | author = David Roth | year = 2006 | title = Rainfall Summary for Tropical Storm Kyle | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | accessdate = 2014-05-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130921190615/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/kyle2002.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/kyle2002.html | archivedate = 2013-09-21 }}</ref>。位于[[三角_(北卡罗莱纳州|罗利-达勒姆]]的一个气象站在两天内记录下的降雨量总计达到147毫米，创下继1999年[[飓风弗洛伊德|飓风弗洛伊德]]以来的新纪录<ref name="usda">{{cite web | author = National Agricultural Statistics Service (United States Department of Agriculture) | date = 2002-10-16 | title = National Weather Summary, Vol. 89, No. 42 - October 6–12, 2002 | accessdate = 2014-05-03 | url = http://usda.mannlib.cornell.edu/usda/nass/WWNatSumm//2000s/2002/WWNatSumm-10-16-2002.txt | archive-date = 2006-09-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20060910203543/http://usda.mannlib.cornell.edu/usda/nass/WWNatSumm//2000s/2002/WWNatSumm-10-16-2002.txt | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[马丁县_(北卡罗莱纳州)|马丁县]]因暴雨导致山洪爆发，多条道路因此封闭<ref>{{cite report | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2002 | title = Event Report for North Carolina}}</ref>。该州遭受的风力为中等强度，阵风时速最快的[[秃头岛|秃头岛]]（{{lang|en|Bald Head Island}}）达到79公里。风暴还在该州催生了至少三场龙卷风，其中出现在[[博福特县_(北卡罗莱纳州)|博福特县]][[潘蒂戈_(北卡罗莱纳州)|潘蒂戈]]（{{lang|en|Pantego}}）附近的一场造成两套房屋和一个农庄受到破坏<ref name="tcr" />。

凯尔带来的湿气延伸到[[中大西洋各州|中大西洋各州]]和[[纽约州|纽约州]]南部，产生的降水缓解了这些地区的旱情<ref name="usda" />。整场风暴共计造成了约500万美元（2002年美元，相当于{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|5000000|2002}}}}{{#time:Y}}年美元）的损失<ref name="tcr" />。凯尔没有直接造成人员丧生，但其残留在不列颠群岛近海产生了大浪，导致一人遇难<ref name="gp" />。

== 纪录 ==
飓风凯尔在热带气旋状态下持续了22天，气象部门当时在实际操作中认为这创下了持续时间第三长的[[北大西洋热带气旋|北大西洋热带气旋]]新纪录<ref name="tcr" />，仅次于1971年的[[飓风金格|飓风金格]]（27.25天）和1969年的[[1969年飓风因加|飓风因加]]（24.75天）<ref>{{cite web | author = Franklin & Blake | year = 2002 | title = Tropical Storm Kyle Discussion Seventy | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-05-03 | archivedate = 2012-10-25 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025094402/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.070.html | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al122002.discus.070.html }}</ref>。不过，2004年对大西洋飓风数据库的一次更新结果表明，1899年的圣西里亚科飓风才是[[信史|有纪录以来]]持续时间最长的大西洋热带气旋，凯尔的位置也因此降到第四。2012年9月，[[飓风纳丁|飓风纳丁]]的持续时长达到22.25天，凯尔的排名再降到第五。截止2014年4月，凯尔仍然是有纪录以来仅有的一个五次达到热带风暴强度的大西洋热带气旋。<ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2013-040114.txt | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2014-04-01 | accessdate = 2014-05-03 | archivedate = 2014-04-09 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140409092642/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2013-040114.txt | deadurl = no }}</ref>

